{"tid":1437842,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港 時代革命！ 聽唔聽到我地嘅聲音？","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T17:48:50.000Z","uid":164192,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56e350e8cb7daf0560e16c1d96bca8574398b7f6","tid":1437842,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0YhtHt-8FBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0YhtHt-8FBY&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=b10435b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0YhtHt-8FBY</a> (歌詞 - 字幕功能）<br />\n<br />\n對真正嘅自由、民主有價值觀分野，可能係藍黃之分；<br />\n但係連黑白都無視，可能係你仲扮緊瞓唔肯醒。<br />\n<br />\n如果你睇某一部份、某件事、某段片，你會覺得好混亂，點解會有咁大嘅反對聲音？<br />\n但係如果你肯用一條長時間線去睇成個運動，暸解前因後果，你會明白極權已經完全踩過界。<br />\n<br />\n我愛國更愛香港，但係我從來唔愛獨裁政權！愛國唔係要愛黨！<br />\n今次香港玩完，全中國嘅人權水平將會衝破最低點，將會有更多更瘋狂嘅手段打壓一切異見，<br />\n連香港濫權情況都去到今時今日嘅地步，依個地方仲有咩未來可言？<br />\n<br />\n聽日 810 大埔，後日 811 深水埗 星戰。<br />\n有緣見。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n沒有大台，自由意志。<br />\n各有各做，永不割席。"},{"pid":"7fe1a232f36469a70912db1f0995fc3baf7c125c","tid":1437842,"uid":137265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"小弟諗左啲set deadline嘅新思路<br />\n唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實點解大家放棄左deadline?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1437366/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1437366/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家追一追文（大概5頁就夠）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終我直接copy出黎有啲野唔清晰<br />\n要靠大家互相質問討論先補充到"},{"pid":"952fc32d5afd14df83e2e16e5162933f86059269","tid":1437842,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"天佑香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0daf10553ce601965a595a6afbeecf5b8819901","tid":1437842,"uid":199339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"聽日大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436835/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436835/page/1</a><br />\n入黎幫手推記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b43ed7165b00eba92d4bbe230c95eba5e3ddf05","tid":1437842,"uid":230621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faaca4b1d356a90341d30146f2a38ca16b2d3bf","tid":1437842,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0daf10553ce601965a595a6afbeecf5b8819901","tid":1437842,"uid":199339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"聽日大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436835/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436835/page/1</a><br />\n入黎幫手推記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"大埔見！雖然岩岩黃大仙已經有衝突，但係聽日重點係大埔！"},{"pid":"ee1eba2b69f80ac8f6f2bc7cd3dbc7322ab237ec","tid":1437842,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:58:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"